Second of all, now I can't stop thinking about ways you could do this and have it actually stick to the wall without breaking apart. Maybe metal wires? Through the middle of each finger and attached to a suction cup? Maybe attached to a metal or wood base that has a screw so you can screw it into the wall?
Either way, I agree with Julien, get that cursed hand out of your house, save yourselves.
